comments: Caldwell-Pope (WAS) defends over the screen and makes marginal contact with Markkanen (CLE) as they disengage.
Caldwell-Pope (WAS) dislodges the ball from Markkanen (CLE) in the post before incidental contact occurs.
Goodwin (CLE) establishes himself in a screening position in Caldwell-Pope's (WAS) path and does not deliver contact.
Smith (WAS) makes marginal contact with Allen (CLE) underneath the basket and he's able to move through the contact to gather the loose ball.
Smith (WAS) is the last person to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds. The possession is correctly awarded to CLE.
Goodwin (CLE) is already in Gafford's (WAS) path and makes marginal contact as they disengage.
Mobley (CLE) loses control of the ball prior to incidental contact occurring from Gafford (WAS) on the driving shot attempt.
Mobley (CLE) naturally loses control of the ball during his shooting motion, allowing him to legally regain control of the ball.
Okoro (CLE) makes marginal contact with Kuzma (WAS) off-ball that does not affect his ability to get to the pass.
Okoro (CLE) retracts his resting arm from Kuzma's (WAS) body as Kuzma enters his upward shooting motion.
Allen (CLE) establishes himself in a screening position in Caldwell-Pope's (WAS) path and absorbs the contact.
Allen (CLE) establishes himself in a screening position in Smith's (WAS) path and absorbs the contact.
Gafford (WAS) makes marginal contact with Goodwin's (CLE) arm after the release of his driving shot attempt.
Kuzma (WAS) initiates contact to Allen's (CLE) upper body and the contact affects his ability to retrieve the loose ball.
Okoro (CLE) legally contests Kuzma's (WAS) jump shot attempt.
Smith (WAS) makes contact with Allen's (CLE) arm that affects his SQBR.
Kispert (WAS) is already in Okoro's (CLE) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Gafford (WAS) establishes himself in a screening position in Markkanen's (CLE) path and makes marginal contact as they disengage.
Kuzma (WAS) extends his off-arm slightly into Okoro (CLE) on the perimeter, and the contact is marginal.
Okoro (CLE) cleanly dislodges the ball from Kuzma (WAS) during his drive before incidental contact occurs.
Allen (CLE) and Gafford (WAS) engage and disengage with one another during rebounding.
Kispert (WAS) commits a take foul on Goodwin (CLE).
Smith (WAS) hands off the ball in Okoro's (CLE) path and makes marginal contact as they disengage.
Markkanen (CLE) legally contest Kuzma's (WAS) jump shot attempt.
Gafford (WAS) makes marginal contact with Allen (CLE) underneath the basket and disengages as Allen gathers the loose ball.
Gafford (WAS) commits a take foul on Mobley (CLE).
Gafford (WAS) establishes himself in a screening position in Mobley's (CLE) path and makes marginal contact as they disengage.
